reviewText: Arrived timely. DVD was a gift for my great niece. She loves it.

Buyers should note that this movie content is not the "Lord's Prayer" as in the model prayer taught by Jesus.  It is about the prayer of Jesus in the Garden of Gethsemane just before his arrest and subsequent crucifixion.
This DVD was made by the best..working once for Disney, the quality is excellent. Easy to split up in teaching episodes.
Another great addition to the library, replacing a VHS copy.  Great, but pricey.
